{fgbg ry}                                  Trivia Game{eol}
{fgbg cn}
                         Welcome to the Trivial quiz game{fg w}

     Initially you will be asked what you wish to gamble for:

           a) Your upload/download ratio
           b) Your online time
           c) Not gamble for anything except a high score{fg g}

  Everytime you answer a question correctly your score increases by 1 point
  For scores below 5: You lose 1 download for each point below 5 or
                      lose 5 minutes online time for each point below 5
  For scores above 5: You gain 1 download for each point above 5 or
                      gain 5 minutes online time for each point above 5{fg r}

  NB: Don't worry you won't end up with a negative ratio or online time
           q quits the game without affecting your ratios{_>0023}